#: ./doc/security-guide/ch048_key-management.xml:11(para)
msgid "It shall support the creation of keys, and their secure saving (with a service master-key). Some of the design questions still being debated are how much of the Key Management Interchange Protocol (KMIP) to support, key formats, and certificate management. The key manager will be pluggable to facilitate deployments that need a third-party Hardware Security Module (HSM)."
