#: ./doc/security-guide/ch017_threat-models-confidence-and-confidentiality.xml:93(para)
msgid "Given the complexity of the OpenStack components and the number of deployment possibilities, you must take care to ensure that each component gets the appropriate configuration of SSL certificates, keys, and CAs. Subsequent sections discuss the following services:"
